description: Thousands of migrants trying to get into the EU remain in the border zone between the two countries.
title: Turkish police move to stop Greece pushing migrants back
title_page: Turkish police move to stop Greece pushing migrants back - BBC News
maintext: Meanwhile, Greece is struggling to cope with more than 20,000 asylum seekers on the island of Lesbos who are living in squalid, overcrowded camps. There has been local hostility towards new arrivals trying to come ashore from nearby Turkey.
